    v1.16

liblockfile (1.16)

  * lockfile.c: remove all the permission checking in the normal case.
    Only if creating the tempfile / removing the lockfile returns EACCESS,
    check to see if this is a mail-lockfile, if so launch helper.
  * dotlockfile.c: use same mail-lockfile check as lockfile.c, but a
    bit more strict.
  * dotlockfile: actually honor -q flag (quiet) everywhere

